Posts.Content: Suzi18 wrote: Hello everyone, this is my first post here. Last week I went for my annual exam (I hadn't had an annual in 7 years) and during the breast examination the ARNP found a dense mass in my left breast. She ordered a mammogram along with an ultrasound which I had done Thursday 4/11. I'm waiting for the results and trying not to worry, but it's like asking me not to look at the pink elephant in the room.  Any advice, words of wisdom are truly appreciated. God Bless~ Suzi Log in to post a reply

Posts.Content: Apr 15, 2013 04:36PM Suzi18 wrote: Thank you for your response. I heard back today and all was normal in my mammogram/ultrasound.
